rows.label: tlk41700121_04_msg0001
rows.name:
That Cordell Village, the one that got
occupied by bandits... Yeah, I don't
think there's any hope of it recovering.

rows.label: tlk41700121_04_msg0002
rows.name:
Pretty much all the residents were
killed, and the buildings were ruined
as well. What can you do at that point?

rows.label: tlk41700121_04_msg0003
rows.name:
It was only a small village, without even
a military station, but still...people sure
do some awful things, huh.

rows.label: tlk41700121_04_msg0004
rows.name:
I can only pray for the people of
Cordell to rest in peace.
